\c 1
\s Ukulwa kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli lamaKhanani
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi emva kokufa kukaJoshuwa abantwana bakoIsrayeli babuza iN\nd kosi\x + Nani 27.21.\x*\nd* besithi: Ngubani ozasenyukelela ukuyamelana lamaKhanani kuqala\x + 20.18.\x* ukulwa emelene labo?
\v 2 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: UJuda uzakwenyuka; khangelani, ngilinikele ilizwe esandleni sakhe.
\v 3 UJuda wasesithi kuSimeyoni umfowabo: Yenyuka lami enkathweni yami ukuze silwe simelene lamaKhanani; lami-ke ngizahamba lawe enkathweni yakho\x + 1.17.\x*. USimeyoni wasehamba laye.
\v 4 UJuda wasesenyuka, njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yanikela amaKhanani lamaPerizi esandleni sabo; bawatshaya eBezeki\x + 1 Sam. 11.8.\x*, amadoda azinkulungwane ezilitshumi.
\v 5 Basebefica uAdoni-Bezeki eBezeki, balwa bemelene laye, bawatshaya amaKhanani lamaPerizi.
\v 6 Kodwa uAdoni-Bezeki wabaleka, baxotshana laye, bambamba, baquma izithupha zezandla zakhe lamazwane akhe amakhulu.
\v 7 UAdoni-Bezeki wasesithi: Amakhosi angamatshumi ayisikhombisa aqunywe izithupha zezandla zawo lezenyawo zawo ayedobha ngaphansi kwetafula lami. Njengokwenza kwami\x + Levi 24.19. 1 Sam. 15.33. Jak. 2.13. Hlu.1.21.\x*, ngokunjalo uNkulunkulu ungiphindisele. Basebemusa eJerusalema, wafela khona.
\v 8 Abantwana bakoJuda balwa-ke bemelene leJerusalema\x + Josh. 15.63.\x*, bayithumba, bayitshaya ngobukhali benkemba, lomuzi bawuthungela ngomlilo.
\p
\v 9 Emva kwalokho-ke abantwana bakoJuda behla ukuyakulwa bemelene lamaKhanani ayehlala entabeni leningizimu lesihotsheni.
\v 10 UJuda wasehamba wamelana lamaKhanani ayehlala eHebroni\x + Josh. 10.36; 11.21; 14.13,15; 15.13,14. Josh. 21.11.\x*; lebizo leHebroni kuqala kwakuyiKiriyathi-Arba; batshaya uSheshayi\x + Nani 13.22.\x* loAhimani loTalimayi.
\v 11 Basuka lapho baya bamelana labahlali beDebiri\x + Josh. 10.38.\x*. Lebizo leDebiri kuqala kwakuyiKiriyathi-Seferi.
\v 12 UKalebi\x + 1.15, Josh. 15.16,17,18,19.\x* wasesithi: Ozatshaya iKiriyathi-Seferi, ayithumbe, ngizamnika uAkisa indodakazi yami ibe ngumka\add khe\add*.
\v 13 UOthiniyeli indodana kaKenazi umfowabo kaKalebi, owayemncane kulaye\x + 3.9.\x*, waseyithumba; wasemnika uAkisa indodakazi yakhe ukuba ngumka\add khe\add*.
\v 14 Kwasekusithi ekufikeni kwakhe wamkhuthaza ukuthi acele kuyise insimu; wasesehla kubabhemi, uKalebi wasesithi kuye: Ulani?
\v 15 Wasesithi kuye: Ngipha isibusiso. Njengoba ungiphe ilizwe leningizimu, ngipha njalo imithombo yamanzi. UKalebi wasemnika imithombo engaphezulu lemithombo engaphansi.
\p
\v 16 Abantwana bomKeni\x + 4.11,17; 5.24. 1 Sam. 15.6. 1 Lan. 2.55.\x*, uyisezala kaMozisi, basebesenyuka besuka emzini wamalala\x + Dute. 34.3.\x*, belabantwana bakoJuda, baya enkangala yakoJuda, eseningizimu kweAradi\x + Nani 21.1; 33.40. Josh. 12.14.\x*; baya bahlala phakathi kwabantu\x + Nani 10.29,30,31,32.\x*.
\v 17 UJuda wasehamba loSimeyoni umfowabo\x + 1.3.\x*, bawatshaya amaKhanani ayehlala eZefathi\x + 2 Lan. 14.10.\x*, bayitshabalalisa. Ngakho ibizo lomuzi lathiwa yiHorma\x + Josh. 19.4. Nani 14.45; 21.3.\x*.
\v 18 UJuda wasethumba iGaza\x + Josh. 11.22. Hlu.3.3. Josh. 15.47.\x* lomngcele wayo, leAshikeloni\x + 14.19. 1 Sam. 6.17. 2 Sam. 1.20. Jer. 25.20; 47.5,7. Amos 1.8. Zef. 2.4,7. Zek. 9.5.\x* lomngcele wayo, leEkhironi\x + Josh. 15.11.\x* lomngcele wayo.
\v 19 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisiba loJuda\x + 1.2,22.\x*, wadla ilifa lezintaba, kodwa weyengelakubaxotsha elifeni abahlali besigodi, ngoba babelezinqola zensimbi\x + Josh. 11.6.\x*.
\v 20 Basebenika uKalebi\x + Nani 14.24. Dute. 1.36. Hlu.1.10.\x* iHebroni, njengokutsho kukaMozisi; wasexotsha elifeni esuka lapho amadodana amathathu kaAnaki.
\v 21 Kodwa abantwana bakoBhenjamini kabawaxotshanga elifeni amaJebusi ayehlala eJerusalema\x + Josh. 18.28. Hlu.1.8.\x*; ngakho amaJebusi ahlala labantwana bakoBhenjamini eJerusalema kuze kube lamuhla\x + 2 Sam.5.6.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Lendlu kaJosefa, labo benyukela eBhetheli; njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yayilabo.
\v 23 Indlu kaJosefa yasithuma inhloli eBhetheli\x + Nani 13.2,21,32; 14.6,34. Josh.2.1; 7.2. Hlu.18.2.\x*; lebizo lomuzi kuqala laliyiLuzi\x + Gen. 28.19; 35.1,6; 48.3. Josh. 7.2; 18.13,22.\x*.
\v 24 Abalindi basebebona umuntu ephuma emzini, bathi kuye: Akusitshengise indlela yokungena emzini, besesikwenzela umusa\x + Josh. 2.12,14; 8.35.\x*.
\v 25 Esebatshengise indlela yokungena emzini, bawutshaya umuzi ngobukhali benkemba, kodwa lowomuntu losapho lwakhe lonke babayekela bahamba.
\v 26 Lowomuntu wasesiya elizweni lamaHethi\x + Josh. 1.4. 1 Kho. 10.29. 2 Kho.7.6. 2 Lan.1.17.\x*, wakha umuzi, wabiza ibizo lawo \add ngokuthi\add* yiLuzi; yilelo ibizo lawo kuze kube lamuhla.
\p
\v 27 UManase kaxotshanga-ke iBeti-Sheyani lemizana yayo\x + 1.27,28, Josh. 17.11,12,13.\x*, leThahanakhi lemizana yayo, labahlali beDori lemizana yayo, labahlali beIbileyamu lemizana yayo, labahlali beMegido lemizana yayo; kodwa amaKhanani afuna ukuhlala kulelolizwe.
\v 28 Kwasekusithi uIsrayeli eselamandla wawamisa amaKhanani kusibhalo, kodwa kawaxotshanga lokuwaxotsha elifeni.
\p
\v 29 UEfrayimi kawaxotshanga-ke elifeni amaKhanani ayehlala eGezeri\x + Josh. 16.10. Josh. 10.33.\x*, kodwa amaKhanani ahlala eGezeri phakathi kwabo\x + 1.30,32. Hlab. 106.34,35.\x*.
\p
\v 30 UZebuluni kabaxotshanga elifeni abahlali beKitroni labahlali beNahaloli\x + Josh. 19.15; 21.35.\x*, kodwa amaKhanani ahlala phakathi kwabo, aba yizibhalwa.
\p
\v 31 UAsheri kabaxotshanga elifeni abahlali beAko labahlali beSidoni\x + Josh. 19.28,29,30. Josh. 12.18.\x* leAhilabi leAkizibi\x + Josh. 19.28,29,30. Josh. 12.18.\x* leHeliba leAfiki\x + Josh. 19.28,29,30. Josh. 12.18.\x* leRehobi\x + Josh. 19.28,29,30. Josh. 12.18.\x*;
\v 32 kodwa abakoAsheri bahlala phakathi kwamaKhanani\x + 1.29.\x* abahlali belizwe, ngoba kabawaxotshanga elifeni.
\p
\v 33 UNafithali kabaxotshanga elifeni abahlali beBeti-Shemeshi\x + Josh. 19.38.\x* labahlali beBeti-Anathi\x + Josh. 19.38.\x*, kodwa wahlala phakathi kwamaKhanani\x + 1.29.\x*, abahlali belizwe; kodwa abahlali beBeti-Shemeshi labeBeti-Anathi baba yizibhalwa kubo\x + 1.28,30,35.\x*.
\p
\v 34 AmaAmori asebafuqela abantwana bakoDani entabeni\x + Josh. 19.47. Hlu.18.1.\x*, ngoba kawabavumelanga ukwehlela esigodini.
\v 35 Kodwa amaAmori ayefuna ukuhlala entabeni yeHeresi\x + Josh. 19.41. Hlu.2.9.\x* eAjaloni\x + Josh. 19.42.\x* leShahalibimi\x + Josh. 19.42.\x*, kodwa isandla sendlu kaJosefa saba nzima, aba yizibhalwa.
\v 36 Umngcele wamaAmori wawusukela emqansweni weAkirabimi, uvela edwaleni usiya phezulu.
